# The `NVPTXGenericMCSymbolRefExpr` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

A wrapper for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcsymbolrefexpr">MCSymbolRefExpr</a> that tells the assembly printer that the symbol should be enclosed by generic(). <a href="#details">More...</a>
